Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.38,0:00:42.74,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, everyone...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.74,0:00:44.66,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,It's all because I'm filthy.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:44.66,0:00:47.18,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.45,0:00:51.28,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,{\an8}The cursed girl, Asahi Haruka?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.28,0:00:52.25,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:52.25,0:00:55.53,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,We got a letter in the\NMonster Mailbox Shizuru set up.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:56.53,0:01:00.54,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Let's see... "Are you all familiar\Nwith the story of Asahi Haruka?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:01.56,0:01:05.29,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,If you attempt to investigate\Nher and disturb her slumber,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:05.29,0:01:07.39,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,you will be placed under her curse.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:09.46,0:01:11.49,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,In a certain forest, there was an orphanage.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:13.23,0:01:16.52,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,After a girl called Asahi Haruka arrived there,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:16.52,0:01:19.01,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,strange things began to occur.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:20.14,0:01:22.43,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Windows and mirrors would shatter on their own,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:22.43,0:01:25.44,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,and the pets would suddenly pass away...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.44,0:01:28.82,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Before long, the children\Nand teachers were affected, too...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.47,0:01:33.40,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,In the end, the orphanage was closed down."
Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.89,0:01:38.76,Default,Aka,0,0,0,,This story sounds somewhat familiar.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:38.76,0:01:40.43,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,"Seven years ago,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:40.43,0:01:44.02,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,a boy from that orphanage transferred into\Nthe school I was attending at the time,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:44.02,0:01:47.61,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Kazamatsuri 7th Municipal Elementary School.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:47.61,0:01:51.59,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,A few days after he told us\Nthe story of Asahi Haruka,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.12,0:01:55.09,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,he died of a strange, unknown illness.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.76,0:01:58.99,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,He was cursed for disturbing her slumber.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.60,0:02:03.10,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,His name was Kishida Ryuugo,\Nand he was in Class 4-1."
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.48,0:02:05.55,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Things got awfully specific all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.55,0:02:06.31,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.65,0:02:08.33,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,If he was in 4th grade seven years ago,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.33,0:02:10.25,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,then he would've been the same age as us.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.25,0:02:12.74,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure Yoshino is\Nfrom 7th Elementary, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.74,0:02:14.63,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Corroborating this story\Nshould be a simple matter,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.63,0:02:16.42,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,and then I'll get to touch Prez's boo—
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.86,0:02:20.82,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,By the way, where are Shizuru and the class rep?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.44,0:02:25.47,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,Maybe coming here feels awkward,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.47,0:02:27.21,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,considering what happened yesterday.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.21,0:02:29.58,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Are you still fighting?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.58,0:02:32.09,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,It's not like we fought or anything...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.79,0:02:34.09,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.09,0:02:35.39,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Before investigating,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.39,0:02:38.03,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,we've first gotta fix things\Nbetween Chihaya and the class rep.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.98,0:02:42.55,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Why Lucia wears gloves?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.55,0:02:43.49,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.49,0:02:46.88,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Sure, she may be a clean-freak,\Nbut it seems a little excessive.{I forgot to hyphenate in ep04}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.34,0:02:50.93,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,And given what happened yesterday,\NI figured I should at least ask why.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.66,0:02:54.74,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Kotarou...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.45,0:02:57.82,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Are you Lucia's friend?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.35,0:02:59.57,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I would think so.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.81,0:03:04.58,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Then I don't mind telling you Lucia's secret.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.13,0:03:06.17,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Secret?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.23,0:03:11.05,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,So long as you will be Lucia's friend forever...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.26,0:03:19.25,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,The class rep's secret, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.85,0:03:26.35,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,What do you want?\NI'm a little occupied at the moment.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.35,0:03:27.92,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Oh my, out on a date?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.92,0:03:29.13,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.13,0:03:32.29,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,By the way, you went to 7th Elementary, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.29,0:03:34.11,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,In 4th grade, which class were you in?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.55,0:03:36.36,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,What's it to you?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.46,0:03:41.13,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'm not playing along.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.13,0:03:44.16,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,Disturbing the dead ain't my thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.16,0:03:46.91,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Does that mean a transfer student named Kishida
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.91,0:03:49.00,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,really did die due to some\Nstrange, unknown illness?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.00,0:03:50.20,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,Like I'd know!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.20,0:03:52.22,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,And I wouldn't tell you even if I did.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.22,0:03:56.59,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,I may have never spoken to him,\Nbut he was still my friend.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.59,0:03:57.48,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.48,0:03:58.55,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Sorry about this.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.83,0:04:00.96,Default - Alt,Yoshi,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wait. Why are you sticking your nose into all this?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.53,0:04:03.44,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Something about it just stuck out in my mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.44,0:04:05.64,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,This case just doesn't sit right with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.18,0:04:07.22,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,Tennouji.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.87,0:04:09.69,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,I'll give you one warning.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.21,0:04:12.14,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,If things start looking dicey, back off.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.14,0:04:13.14,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,What do you mean, dicey?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.14,0:04:15.64,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,If the glass shatters, watch your back.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.64,0:04:16.49,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Glass?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.49,0:04:17.37,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.37,0:04:19.03,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,That's all I'm going to say on the matter.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.21,0:04:31.81,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,This is all the help I can give you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.81,0:04:34.42,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,Get by on your own luck from here on out.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.39,0:04:38.37,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,That roster is a part of my history.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.37,0:04:40.84,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,Give it back as soon as you're done with it.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.86,0:04:45.04,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Thank you, Yoshino.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.04,0:04:47.85,Default,Nishi,0,0,0,,Could you make copies of this for the whole class?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.85,0:04:48.78,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.78,0:04:51.35,Default,Nishi,0,0,0,,I'll lend you my copy card.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.20,0:04:57.48,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Class Rep!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.48,0:04:58.61,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,What is it, Tennouji?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.43,0:05:01.09,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Hey! This isn't for personal use!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.09,0:05:02.11,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,It's just one copy.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.11,0:05:03.11,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Pretend you never saw it.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.11,0:05:04.41,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.86,0:05:07.37,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,What are you copying?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.98,0:05:09.48,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Sorry, but it's a secret.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.48,0:05:12.25,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,If you knew, you could be cursed.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.25,0:05:14.25,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Did you say "cursed"?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.06,0:05:17.00,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Owe ya, Class Rep!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.34,0:05:18.56,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.35,0:05:25.08,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I guess I should give everyone a call.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.08,0:05:26.26,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Wait, Tennouji!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.60,0:05:29.35,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,You left this in the tray.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.35,0:05:30.51,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,It's yours, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.31,0:05:37.78,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.78,0:05:39.40,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I don't remember copying anything like—
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.73,0:05:46.08,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,{\i1}If the glass shatters, watch your back.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.11,0:05:48.66,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,It couldn't be, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.66,0:05:50.45,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,It couldn't be what?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.45,0:05:51.83,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.83,0:05:54.10,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,What are you plotting this time?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.10,0:05:57.58,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Depending on your answer,\NTennouji Kotarou, I might have to...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.84,0:06:04.74,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,So you're telling me that both\Nthe note and the shattered glass
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.74,0:06:06.97,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,are warnings from Asahi Haruka?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.97,0:06:08.47,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.81,0:06:11.85,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,The copier must've spat out the wrong sheet.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.85,0:06:13.47,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,But that note...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.47,0:06:15.11,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Probably just used paper.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.11,0:06:17.78,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Maybe a recycled sheet got mixed in?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.78,0:06:18.87,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.87,0:06:22.48,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,As for the windows, someone must\Nhave thrown a rock or something.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.48,0:06:24.86,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,You don't believe it's a curse?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.86,0:06:29.24,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Well, you could say I have a reason\Nfor not wanting to in this case.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.24,0:06:32.58,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Anyway, I want to prove there's\Nno such thing as curses
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.58,0:06:34.74,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,and clear that girl's name.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.27,0:06:36.50,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Clear her name?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.50,0:06:41.33,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,If Asahi Haruka is being hurt\Nby all this even to this day,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.33,0:06:43.25,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,as a part of the occult club,\NI just can't leave it as-is.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.75,0:06:46.51,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,You have a point...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.51,0:06:48.29,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Then it's settled.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.29,0:06:52.26,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Let's close the book on this cheap horror story!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.54,0:06:55.26,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.85,0:07:04.02,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Close the book, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.30,0:07:08.30,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. The forecast did say it was going to rain.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.78,0:07:14.91,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Why do you wake me?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.93,0:07:15.79,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.08,0:07:19.93,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Why do you wake me?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.58,0:07:27.20,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,We are both burdened by the same sorrow, too...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.97,0:07:32.45,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Do not wake me...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.45,0:07:33.93,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Or else...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.60,0:07:36.03,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,You will...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.91,0:07:45.48,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.07,0:07:48.53,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,Th-The glass!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.53,0:07:50.49,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Um, are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.49,0:07:52.06,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,That's why I said no!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.06,0:07:53.53,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,It's just like four years ago!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.53,0:07:55.95,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,The curse hasn't gone away!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.95,0:07:57.19,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Uh, hang on!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.50,0:07:59.88,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.44,0:08:03.39,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}Strangely, every person I called got really scared
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.39,0:08:05.00,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}the second I brought up Asahi Haruka
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.52,0:08:07.94,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}and refused to answer any questions.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.94,0:08:10.28,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}In addition, after my call,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.28,0:08:13.88,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}they all mysteriously experienced\Ntheir windows or mirrors breaking...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.59,0:08:17.61,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I left contacting the girls up to the class rep...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.17,0:08:19.93,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,All right, one more person!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.04,0:08:25.32,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Oh, is this Wada Kenji-kun's residence?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.32,0:08:26.34,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Sorry to call so late—
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.34,0:08:28.95,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Huh? He isn't there?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.33,0:08:39.16,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,That's for the best.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.05,0:08:44.75,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Remember our suffering...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.58,0:08:47.88,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,N-No.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.27,0:08:51.35,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,I decided to face it!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.35,0:08:52.88,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,That is impossible.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.61,0:08:56.38,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,After all, we really are...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.97,0:08:59.30,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,cursed.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.35,0:09:08.85,Default,Koto,0,0,0,,I wonder if Class Rep is absent?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.60,0:09:14.61,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,I thought I would get to\Napologize to her today for sure...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.62,0:09:21.65,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,It's not like her to be absent without leave.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.65,0:09:23.62,Default,Ino,0,0,0,,Hi there, Tennouji-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.00,0:09:24.87,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Inoue.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.87,0:09:28.38,Default,Ino,0,0,0,,I caught wind that you're after a dangerous scoop?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.38,0:09:29.73,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.68,0:09:35.45,Default,Ino,0,0,0,,About that story... Quite frankly,\Nit's considered off-limits among us reporters.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.45,0:09:35.88,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.24,0:09:38.97,Default,Ino,0,0,0,,Someone who was researching\Nit got into an accident.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.97,0:09:42.39,Default,Ino,0,0,0,,This has a column written by him.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.75,0:09:43.77,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Accident?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.77,0:09:47.46,Default,Ino,0,0,0,,If you call yourself my rival,\Npursuing the mysteries of Kazamatsuri,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.46,0:09:49.31,Default,Ino,0,0,0,,then handle the rest on your own.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.31,0:09:51.77,Default,Ino,0,0,0,,Just to let you know, you owe me one.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.81,0:09:51.77,Default - Alt,Kota,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.89,0:09:57.95,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Baraki?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.64,0:10:05.60,Default,Bara,0,0,0,,This is a recording from\N7th Elementary Class 4-1's reunion.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.60,0:10:08.54,Default,Bara,0,0,0,,All the glass in the entire venue\Nshattered outta nowhere.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.95,0:10:10.59,Default,Bara,0,0,0,,And, on the way back from the event,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.59,0:10:13.07,Default,Bara,0,0,0,,a huge billboard fell right in front of me.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.07,0:10:16.31,Default,Bara,0,0,0,,If it had actually hit me, I'd be dead for sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.31,0:10:17.99,Default,Bara,0,0,0,,I hear the rumors exaggerated it somewhat
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.99,0:10:20.80,Default,Bara,0,0,0,,and say I got seriously hurt, though!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.46,0:10:24.55,Default,Bara,0,0,0,,In the end, all I was able to get out of anyone
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.55,0:10:26.39,Default,Bara,0,0,0,,was that late Kishida Ryuugo lived in
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.39,0:10:29.77,Default,Bara,0,0,0,,an orphanage called\N"The Santa Brosia Peace Garden."
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.23,0:10:38.09,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Do not wake me.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.29,0:10:50.54,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.68,0:10:59.55,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Class Rep?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.55,0:11:03.17,Default,Luc2,0,0,0,,Do not wake me.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.17,0:11:06.10,Default,Luc2,0,0,0,,This is your final warning.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.80,0:11:07.93,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Class Rep!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.26,0:11:12.21,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.96,0:11:14.14,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.24,0:11:19.45,Default,Teach,0,0,0,,Hang in there.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.45,0:11:21.18,Default,Teach,0,0,0,,I'm here for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.18,0:11:23.40,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,No, Sensei...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.40,0:11:25.08,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,If you touch me...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:25.82,0:11:26.96,Default,Teach,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.02,0:11:34.13,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,It was a dream?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.63,0:11:36.83,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.27,0:11:38.55,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.55,0:11:39.97,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,You came to?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.97,0:11:42.47,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Tennouji?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.23,0:11:44.25,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.25,0:11:45.47,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,That's what happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.47,0:11:47.95,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Uh, about your clothes, um...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.95,0:11:49.58,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I thought you would catch a cold.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.58,0:11:53.48,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I-I didn't look, a-and I didn't touch\Nyour skin or anything, either.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.93,0:11:55.13,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.13,0:11:56.48,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.31,0:12:05.24,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Watch.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.36,0:12:10.99,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Wh-What just happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.58,0:12:13.68,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,It's the curse of Asahi Haruka.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.68,0:12:15.73,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,When I touch plants, they wither.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.02,0:12:18.13,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.09,0:12:20.68,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Is this my fault?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.68,0:12:22.71,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Were you cursed in retribution
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.71,0:12:24.88,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,for me not giving up on my investigation?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.34,0:12:27.22,Default,luc,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it, Tennouji.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.80,0:12:30.14,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Even if that were the case,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.65,0:12:32.26,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,it would change nothing for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.28,0:12:38.77,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Lucia experienced unfortunate\Nincidents when she was young.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.14,0:12:41.98,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,She made the plants and\Nanimals raised in her class
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.98,0:12:45.28,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,wither and die one after another.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.28,0:12:47.81,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Surely it was just a coincidence?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.81,0:12:53.05,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Lucia convinced herself\Nthat it was her fault, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.05,0:12:55.60,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,She thought it was because\Nher hands were filthy...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.17,0:13:02.04,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,That's why Lucia is too afraid\Nto touch any living thing to this day.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.49,0:13:06.20,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Lucia has faced that trauma\Nhead-on in her own way.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.20,0:13:08.43,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,She's attempted to overcome it.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.84,0:13:13.15,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,And her gloves provide her the most respite.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.20,0:13:18.19,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,I could just wear my gloves forever\Nand never touch anyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.19,0:13:19.99,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Nothing will change.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.50,0:13:21.46,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.98,0:13:22.94,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.54,0:13:25.65,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,So it won't be painful...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.65,0:13:27.70,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,I'm filthy.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.70,0:13:28.91,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,I'm unclean, so—
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.91,0:13:31.20,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,No! You're wrong about that!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.58,0:13:35.42,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,You don't understand!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.42,0:13:38.21,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Not my sorrow, nor Asahi Haruka's suffering!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.68,0:13:42.15,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,I always knew.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.85,0:13:46.67,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,There's no world that can\Naccept people as filthy as us.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.36,0:13:48.22,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.98,0:13:50.99,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,We will live the rest of our lives
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.99,0:13:54.85,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,never touching another person,\Nall alone, in solitude.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.50,0:13:58.85,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,That's how it has to be!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.77,0:14:01.86,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why did it turn out this way?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.43,0:14:04.11,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.47,0:14:14.39,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,This is the entrance to the orphanage?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.39,0:14:17.49,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I've got no choice but to check it out.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.09,0:14:31.59,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}It {\i0}does{\i1} look like children used to be here.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.80,0:14:50.24,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,This is Kishida Ryuugo?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.24,0:14:51.69,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Asahi Haruka is...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.35,0:14:58.58,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Found you, Asahi Haruka.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.58,0:14:59.37,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Or should I say...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.01,0:15:02.53,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Konohana Lucia!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.90,0:15:05.88,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,How did you know it was me?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.28,0:15:07.49,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.49,0:15:08.26,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,The roster?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.26,0:15:09.41,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.41,0:15:13.21,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,The Wada Kenji on this list doesn't\Nlive at this address anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.21,0:15:14.87,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,He moved.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.87,0:15:17.71,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,And yet, the glass in that house shattered, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.71,0:15:19.92,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Surely a curse wouldn't make mistakes, would it?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.61,0:15:23.73,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,The only ones with this roster are Yoshino, myself,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.73,0:15:25.77,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,and you, Class Rep.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.77,0:15:27.30,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.30,0:15:29.33,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,I made quite a pathetic mistake.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.03,0:15:34.78,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,When I made that copy,\Nyou looked at the data left on the copier
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.78,0:15:37.78,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,and figured out what I was\Ntrying to investigate, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.41,0:15:41.79,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,That said, I couldn't figure out\Nhow you shattered all that glass.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.04,0:15:46.22,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.22,0:15:49.15,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,By forging that warning and shattering the glass,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.15,0:15:51.55,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,I tried to get you to stop your investigation,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.14,0:15:54.20,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,but you just wouldn't give up.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.20,0:15:55.05,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Class Rep.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.05,0:15:56.79,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,No, Lucia.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.79,0:15:57.89,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.89,0:16:01.68,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,I can't touch anything alive.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.68,0:16:07.21,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,I was born normal, but was reborn\Nthis way at a certain place.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.21,0:16:08.94,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,"This way"?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.33,0:16:11.92,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,You'll never understand\Nif I simply tell you about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.92,0:16:15.52,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,But the curse residing within this hand is real.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.52,0:16:18.70,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,I can shatter glass without\Nlaying a finger on it, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.00,0:16:22.87,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,The poison that dwells in these hands
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.87,0:16:26.33,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,can take the life of anything\Nthey touch, not just plants.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.42,0:16:29.21,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,I didn't want anyone to know
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.80,0:16:32.59,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,about my hideous past, or my true identity.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.14,0:16:34.41,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.05,0:16:37.35,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,That's the curse's true form?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.35,0:16:41.49,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,This area is still heavily laced with my poison.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.49,0:16:43.16,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,I'm saying this for your own good.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.16,0:16:45.23,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Leave this place immediately and seek treatment.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.23,0:16:46.94,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,You can still make it in time.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.98,0:16:50.27,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Tennouji?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.47,0:16:52.27,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.24,0:16:59.52,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Don't tell me, back then...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.52,0:17:01.47,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,G-Get to the hospital now!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.47,0:17:02.25,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.25,0:17:04.04,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,The hospital can't help anymore...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.04,0:17:05.97,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Tennouji.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.97,0:17:07.95,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,What have I done?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.95,0:17:10.23,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,No, I'm the one who should apologize.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.23,0:17:10.75,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.13,0:17:12.31,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.31,0:17:17.51,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,If only I'd been strong enough to\Nwithstand your poison back then,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.76,0:17:23.02,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I could have prevented you from suffering again.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.02,0:17:24.87,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,That's not your fault—
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.87,0:17:26.20,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.20,0:17:30.24,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,To be honest, I've got an unusual power myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.85,0:17:31.90,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,A power?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.35,0:17:39.99,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you doing, Tennouji?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.43,0:17:42.87,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to rewrite my body.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.47,0:17:45.49,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rewrite it into one that can withstand the poison.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.40,0:18:08.77,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.97,0:18:14.40,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I've accepted Konohana Lucia's world!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.40,0:18:16.73,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.73,0:18:19.76,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,This is my power.\NThat's the only way I can explain it.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.59,0:18:23.13,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,What are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.13,0:18:23.99,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.41,0:18:29.11,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I'm Tennouji Kotarou, Konohana Lucia's friend!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.11,0:18:31.10,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,My friend?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.10,0:18:32.82,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Yeah, so...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.91,0:18:39.08,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Never again say you'll spend your life\Nall alone, never touching anyone...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.08,0:18:40.88,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,It's just too sad.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.69,0:18:44.41,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Tennouji...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.89,0:18:48.51,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,And besides, you're not alone at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.41,0:18:52.92,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,You have Shizuru, you have me,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.92,0:18:54.79,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,and you have everyone at the occult club, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.79,0:18:57.02,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Chihaya and Kotori were worried about you!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.02,0:18:58.65,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,And well, Prez too, probably.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.97,0:19:03.66,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,You know, friends don't let friends be all alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.50,0:19:09.67,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.31,0:19:11.29,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,It's a miracle...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.95,0:19:16.04,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,What's wrong with a miracle or two?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.77,0:19:19.55,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,After all, this is a chapel, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.93,0:19:23.70,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.67,0:19:26.47,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.82,0:19:40.57,Default,Nishi,0,0,0,,Oh dear, are we interrupting?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.57,0:19:42.57,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Wh-Who are you people?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.57,0:19:44.48,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,I-It's all right.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.48,0:19:47.57,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,They're, um... my allies.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.15,0:19:49.08,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Allies?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.50,0:19:54.63,Default,Nishi,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.04,0:19:57.34,Default,Nishi,0,0,0,,That was a surprise.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.34,0:20:01.59,Default,Nishi,0,0,0,,It's hard to believe you're resistant\Nto Lucia-chan's poison by nature.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.59,0:20:02.72,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Forget about that.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.72,0:20:05.36,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Who are you and the others?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.36,0:20:07.34,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,You avoided the question the other day,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.83,0:20:11.79,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,but does Lucia have something to do\Nwith Shizuru's organization, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.79,0:20:13.73,Default,Lic,0,0,0,,You know about Shizuru, too?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.38,0:20:15.69,Default,Nishi,0,0,0,,Guardian.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.69,0:20:17.86,Default,Nishi,0,0,0,,That is our organization.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.86,0:20:20.74,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Nishikujou-san! You can't mention that name!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.74,0:20:23.17,Default,Nishi,0,0,0,,It's better than having him snoop around.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.17,0:20:25.64,Default,Nishi,0,0,0,,This incident made that {\i1}quite{\i0} clear, no?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.64,0:20:26.86,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.29,0:20:33.18,Default,Nishi,0,0,0,,Our organization is gathering people\Nwith special powers for a certain purpose.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.18,0:20:37.12,Default,Nishi,0,0,0,,Lucia-chan and Shizuru-chan\Npossess those special powers.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.58,0:20:39.14,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Special powers?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.88,0:20:43.38,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,So what in the world is this\Norganization trying to do?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.38,0:20:46.39,Default,Nishi,0,0,0,,We're protecting the Earth.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.39,0:20:48.51,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Protecting the Earth?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.51,0:20:53.17,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Right now, Kazamatsuri City\Nis in a volatile situation
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.17,0:20:57.63,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,due to an individual who holds the key\Nto Earth's survival or its destruction.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.63,0:20:59.79,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,That doesn't sound pleasant.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.79,0:21:01.20,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,You believe us?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.20,0:21:04.34,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,All this nonsense about how\NEarth could be destroyed?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.34,0:21:07.91,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Well, I doubt you'd lie in this situation.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.91,0:21:11.41,Default,Nishi,0,0,0,,We call that individual the Key.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.84,0:21:12.78,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,The Key?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.16,0:21:14.55,Default,Nishi,0,0,0,,The Key's existence
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.55,0:21:18.83,Default,Nishi,0,0,0,,could have a profound effect on\Nthe world and all of its religions.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.83,0:21:21.96,Default,Nishi,0,0,0,,As such, we cannot even\Nmake their existence public.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.96,0:21:24.65,Default,Nishi,0,0,0,,To make matters worse,\Nthere are those who would shelter the Key
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.65,0:21:27.63,Default,Nishi,0,0,0,,and advocate that Earth {\i1}should{\i0} perish.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.63,0:21:28.86,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.86,0:21:30.39,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Are they a cult?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.39,0:21:34.81,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,It's an organization we treat with utmost caution,\Nsince they wield considerable power.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.81,0:21:36.65,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,They call themselves Gaia.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.65,0:21:38.03,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Gaia?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.03,0:21:40.95,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,It's a fanatical organization that believes the Key
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.95,0:21:42.53,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,will bring about Earth's regeneration.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.70,0:21:47.59,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but that's all we can tell you right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.59,0:21:51.81,Default,Nishi,0,0,0,,Now you have no choice but to keep this secret.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.81,0:21:54.16,Default,Nishi,0,0,0,,We can trust you to keep quiet about this, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.99,0:21:56.16,Default,Nishi,0,0,0,,Otherwise...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.16,0:21:59.37,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,In that case, I have a condition of my own.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.37,0:22:00.67,Default,Nishi,0,0,0,,Oh, what might that be?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.71,0:22:04.92,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,I want to eat a lunch made by Lucia!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.06,0:22:07.17,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.51,0:22:11.18,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Why a lunch made by me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.18,0:22:13.61,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,By the way, you must wear\Na maid's uniform while doing so!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:13.61,0:22:14.68,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,This is non-negotiable!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:14.68,0:22:17.55,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Y-You reprobate!\NWh-Who would wear something like that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:17.55,0:22:18.90,Default,Kota,0,0,0,,Oh, and also, call me Master—
Dialogue: 10,0:22:18.90,0:22:21.14,Default,Luc,0,0,0,,Don't get carried away!
